# MaxisBot

MaxisBot is a personal AI operator built to convert unstructured thoughts into structured knowledge, actionable plans, and finished products.  
It functions as a cognitive workflow layer integrating an LLM system with an Obsidian knowledge base.

The system is not a conversational assistant.  
It is an operational pipeline: idea capture → organization → planning → execution.

---

## Purpose

Typical failure pattern:
- ideas captured inconsistently
- notes fragmented across tools
- research never reused
- projects abandoned

MaxisBot exists to enforce continuity between thinking and building.

Primary objective:
Transform information into output.

---

## Core Principle

Knowledge without execution has no value.

Obsidian provides persistent storage.  
The LLM provides reasoning.  
MaxisBot coordinates action.

